data.description:
Attention Investors! Don't miss this exceptional opportunity to own a Two-Family Home on Randall Rd in Lewiston. Situated on a SUBDIVIDABLE 1.25-acre lot, this property provides ample space for gardening, entertainment, and unwinding in its tranquil natural surroundings. 

Each unit boasts two spacious bedrooms, with the first-floor unit freshly painted and ready for immediate occupancy. Conveniently located near shopping centers, the Maine Turnpike, Bates College, and a wealth of amenities, this vacant property allows the new owner the flexibility to select their tenants or embark on improvements to unlock its full potential. Seize this chance to shape your investment today!
